thread.title: Synnex Corp Qtrly Adjusted EPS ‍$2.14​

author: Reuters Editorial
title: Synnex Corp Qtrly Adjusted EPS ‍$2.14​
text:
March 29 (Reuters) - Synnex Corp:
* ORATION REPORTS FIRST QUARTER FISCAL 2018 RESULTS * SEES Q2 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $2.25 TO $2.35
* QTRLY ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE ‍$2.14​ * ‍DILUTED EARNINGS PER SHARE IS EXPECTED TO BE IN RANGE OF $1.77 TO $1.87 ON A GAAP BASIS FOR Q2 2018​
* QTRLY REVENUE $4.6 BILLION VERSUS $3.5 BLN‍​ * Q1 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $2.11, REVENUE VIEW $4.47 BILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* Q2 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $2.41, REVENUE VIEW $4.75 BILLION — THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S
* SETS QUARTERLY CASH DIVIDEND OF $0.35PER SHARE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
